Most asked question answered
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
How do I keep my skin radiant and flawless? 
I don't use many products, just a few which have been a constant. One of it is The Natural Age-Control Night Cream by @themomsco. This has been my night cream since quite some time now, and my skin can't get enough of it! 
It has bakuchiol in it - a natural alternative to Retinol - which works on fine lines, evens out skin tone & gives a beautiful glow to the face. 

Oh and can I just say the animal lover in me is thrilled that this brand is cruelty free and peta certified too! 
The Moms Co. is one of my favorite Made In India Skincare brands @malikasadani! And the night cream is a pure bliss!

A definite recommendation to anyone who wants to invest in a good skin care product! 
Surely worth a try! And while you're at it, avail an exclusive discount using the code GAB20 ;) @themomsco #ad shot by @storyin_aminute
